codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. Hōc factō Arīōn in mare ~; sed delphīnus eum in ~ sedentem ad lītus vēxit. Choose from this set of possible answers [ nōbilis appropinquārent rapidī, Īnferōs inde redūceret ignārus nōtus, dīvitiās invidēbant, vītam dōnāvit parcerent, permōtī carmen, dēsiluit dorsō, dēspērāret, appārēre prōtinus maleficium] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'nōbilis appropinquārent rapidī', 'Īnferōs inde redūceret ignārus nōtus', 'dīvitiās invidēbant', 'vītam dōnāvit parcerent', 'permōtī carmen', 'dēsiluit dorsō', 'dēspērāret', 'appārēre prōtinus maleficium']
